OL,3,CStepfather jailed for life for 'rage-
OL,4,Cfilled' murder of five-month-old baby
OL,6,FA father, who was entrusted with the
OL,7,Fsafety of his new partner's five-month-
OL,8,Fold baby, has been jailed for life for
OL,9,Fshaking him to death in a "fit of
OL,10,Frage".
OL,12,FJensen-Lee Dougal died after suffering
OL,13,Fcatastrophic brain damage, numerous
OL,14,Ffractures and extensive retinal
OL,15,Fbleeding to both of his eyes at the
OL,16,Fhands of 29-year-old Thomas Morgan,
OL,17,Ffrom Swansea.
OL,26,@qD@[OUrD@EO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/12
