CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772193821
OL,3,CStepfather jailed for life for 'rage-
OL,4,Cfilled' murder of five-month-old baby
OL,6,FExpert scientific witnesses described
OL,7,FJensen-Lee's injuries as the worst
OL,8,Fthey had seen and akin to a high-
OL,9,Fvelocity traffic accident.
OL,11,FIn March 2024, Jensen-Lee was under
OL,12,Fthe care of Morgan while his mother,
OL,13,FJordan Dougal, was at work.
OL,15,FA court heard Morgan, from Gorseinon,
OL,16,Fwas full of rage after arguing with
OL,17,Fhis former partner on the morning of
OL,18,FJensen-Lee's murder.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772193821
OL,3,CStepfather jailed for life for 'rage-
OL,4,Cfilled' murder of five-month-old baby
OL,6,FText messages between the pair showed
OL,7,FMorgan had called his former partner a
OL,8,F"stinking rat" and "stinking little
OL,9,Fdog".
OL,11,FLater that day, Morgan violently shook
OL,12,FJensen-Lee in an "explosive temper" at
OL,13,Fthe Clydach home he shared with Jordan
OL,14,FDougal.
OL,16,FMorgan contacted Ms Dougal to report
OL,17,Fthat her son was choking and had
OL,18,Fstopped breathing.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@NO]pD@TOUqD@DO]tD@ROUtD@cO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772193821
OL,3,CStepfather jailed for life for 'rage-
OL,4,Cfilled' murder of five-month-old baby
OL,6,FHowever, the court was told that
OL,7,FMorgan delayed calling an ambulance to
OL,8,Fcreate a cover story to hide his crime.
OL,10,FHe finally sought assistance from a
OL,11,Fneighbour, who administered CPR to
OL,12,FJensen-Lee and contacted emergency
OL,13,Fservices.
OL,15,FThe infant was taken to hospital,
OL,16,Fwhere doctors discovered a
OL,17,F"devastating" brain injury.
OL,19,FJensen-Lee was taken off life support
OL,20,Fthe following day, and Morgan was
OL,21,Farrested 10 days later.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/12
