PN,46905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772193821
OL,3,CStepfather jailed for life for 'rage-
OL,4,Cfilled' murder of five-month-old baby
OL,6,FIn a witness impact statement read in
OL,7,Fcourt, Jensen-Lee's mother Jordan
OL,8,FDougal said: "Jensen-Lee loved being
OL,9,Fsung to and loved being cuddled by his
OL,10,Fnanny.
OL,12,F"I never had the chance to hear my son
OL,13,Ftell me he loved me or call me mammy.
OL,15,F"That breach of trust is something I
OL,16,Fstruggle with every day.
OL,18,F"I don't feel I have seen genuine
OL,19,Fremorse from Thomas Morgan for the
OL,20,Flifelong damage he has caused.
OL,26,@pD@NOUtD@AOUwD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772193821
OL,3,CStepfather jailed for life for 'rage-
OL,4,Cfilled' murder of five-month-old baby
OL,6,F"I've been given a life sentence of
OL,7,Fgrief."
OL,9,FThroughout his trial, Morgan denied he
OL,10,Fhad murdered Jensen-Lee, telling the
OL,11,Fcourt that the baby choked on vomit,
OL,12,Fwhich caused him to "panic," leading
OL,13,Fhim to insert his fingers down Jensen-
OL,14,FLee's throat and shake the child.
OL,16,FHowever, a jury determined that Morgan
OL,17,Fhad intentionally inflicted the brutal
OL,18,Finjuries on Jensen-Lee, finding him
OL,19,Fguilty of murder and one count of
OL,20,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,21,Fintent at an earlier hearing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@GO]tD@UOUtD@\O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/12
