PN,46907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772193821
OL,3,CStepfather jailed for life for 'rage-
OL,4,Cfilled' murder of five-month-old baby
OL,6,FAt a sentencing hearing at Swansea
OL,7,FCrown Court on Wednesday, 25 February,
OL,8,FMorgan was sentenced to life in prison
OL,9,Fwith a minimum term of 19 years.
OL,11,FSentencing Morgan, the judge, Mrs
OL,12,FJustice Stacey said: "No sentence this
OL,13,Fcourt gives, and nothing that I can
OL,14,Fsay will make it better for Jensen-
OL,15,FLee's mother and grandparents and
OL,16,Feveryone who knew and loved Jensen-
OL,17,FLee. Their lives have been changed
OL,18,Fforever.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772193821
OL,3,CStepfather jailed for life for 'rage-
OL,4,Cfilled' murder of five-month-old baby
OL,6,F"You came into Jensen-Lee's life when
OL,7,Fyou started a relationship with his
OL,8,Fmother when Jensen-Lee was a few weeks
OL,9,Fold. Jordan Dougal felt lucky you had
OL,10,Fcome into her life.
OL,12,F"You were treated as Jensen-Lee's
OL,13,Fstepfather from the beginning - you
OL,14,Fappeared to have a good bond with him.
OL,16,F"We have no way of knowing what
OL,17,Fhappened on the day of Jensen-Lee's
OL,18,Fmurder, as you have lied to the police
OL,19,Fand everyone you have spoken to since.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772193821
OL,3,CStepfather jailed for life for 'rage-
OL,4,Cfilled' murder of five-month-old baby
OL,6,F"What we do know is that Jensen-Lee
OL,7,Fwoke up shortly before you rang Jordan
OL,8,FDougal, and you shook Jensen-Lee so
OL,9,Fviolently that you caused extensive
OL,10,Finjuries consistent with flailing
OL,11,Flimbs.
OL,13,F"Instead of getting help immediately,
OL,14,Fyou rang Ms Dougal several times and
OL,15,Ftook time to invent an entirely false
OL,16,Faccount of what had happened. You then
OL,17,Fspent the next few hours repeating
OL,18,Fyour false account of Jensen-Lee
OL,19,Fchoking to anyone who would listen.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772193821
OL,3,CStepfather jailed for life for 'rage-
OL,4,Cfilled' murder of five-month-old baby
OL,6,F"The injuries were unsurvivable, and
OL,7,Fnothing could have saved Jensen-Lee.
OL,8,FYou were still acting as the grieving
OL,9,Fstepfather at Jensen-Lee's cremation.
OL,10,FAll along, you knew you caused those
OL,11,Finjuries in a fit of temper, and even
OL,12,Fnow, you can not admit to what you
OL,13,Fhave done."
OL,15,FAfter Morgan was found guilty of
OL,16,Fmurder last month, Detective Chief
OL,17,FInspector Lianne Rees of South Wales
OL,18,FPolice said: "The conviction brings
OL,19,Fsome measure of justice, but in no way
OL,20,Feases the profound heartbreak Jensen-
OL,21,FLee's family continue to endure.
OL,26,@zD@NOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/12
