PN,46911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772193821
OL,3,CStepfather jailed for life for 'rage-
OL,4,Cfilled' murder of five-month-old baby
OL,6,F"I want to pay tribute to the members
OL,7,Fof the public, first responders and
OL,8,Feveryone involved in the desperate
OL,9,Fefforts to save Jensen-Lee's life when
OL,10,Ffaced with the most unimaginable and
OL,11,Ftragic circumstances back in March
OL,12,F2024.
OL,14,F"I also want to acknowledge the
OL,15,Fincredible dignity and strength shown
OL,16,Fby Jensen-Lee's family throughout this
OL,17,Fpainful journey.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/12
