PN,46912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772193821
OL,3,CStepfather jailed for life for 'rage-
OL,4,Cfilled' murder of five-month-old baby
OL,6,F"Lastly, I would like to thank the
OL,7,Finvestigation team, Crown Prosecution
OL,8,FService and Prosecution Counsel for
OL,9,Ftheir continued hard work throughout
OL,10,Fwhat has been a very difficult
OL,11,Finvestigation and trial."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@YO]
